    "body": "## Motivation\n\nFollow-up to #22772 for the B200 ModelOpt diffusion CI coverage. This PR now focuses on preserving generated outputs for the B200 ModelOpt cases and fixing the FLUX.2 NVFP4 CI launch path.\n\n## Modifications\n\n- Removes the BF16 quality-comparison test and related threshold/config plumbing from the B200 suite.\n- Saves generated media artifacts for all ModelOpt diffusion CI cases when `SGLANG_DIFFUSION_ARTIFACT_DIR` is set.\n- Requests 5-second generation for the ModelOpt video CI cases and saves video artifacts with a `_5s.mp4` suffix.\n- Fixes the FLUX.2 NVFP4 CI case to run the base `black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-dev` model with `--transformer-weights-path black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-dev-NVFP4`.\n  - The NVFP4 repo is a raw safetensors export and does not contain a Diffusers `config.json`, so passing it as `--transformer-path` causes the `_class_name`/`config.json` load failure seen in CI.\n- Updates the diffusion quantization docs to match the FLUX.2 NVFP4 loading flow.\n\n## Validation\n\n- Reproduced the FLUX.2 NVFP4 loading failure on H100 without needing NVFP4 kernel execution: resolving `black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-dev-NVFP4` as a transformer component returns an empty config, then `config.pop(\"_class_name\")` raises `KeyError`.\n- `python3 -m isort python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/run_suite.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/gpu_cases.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/test_server_common.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/testcase_configs.py`\n- `python3 -m black python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/run_suite.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/gpu_cases.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/test_server_common.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/testcase_configs.py`\n- `python3 -m ruff check --select=F401,F821 --fix python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/run_suite.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/gpu_cases.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/test_server_common.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/testcase_configs.py`\n- `python3 -m py_compile python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/run_suite.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/gpu_cases.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/test_server_common.py python/sglang/multimodal_gen/test/server/testcase_configs.py`\n- `git diff --check`\n\nB200 end-to-end generation is left to CI.",
